'It (the Goddison Park tie) was a proper Cup game and I feel Tuesday will be exactly the same - two teams wanting to win and to score goals, that will make it really open.

'We always enjoy going to Upton Park and with our sold-out allocation once again, it's one we look forward to.'

 

